#### Description

This dashboard visualizes CloudApp and Identity type events according to the [Microsoft Documentation](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/security/defender/advanced-hunting-deviceevents-table?view=o365-worldwide).  
The data is collected from a configured Event Hub, using the M365 Defender Event datastream.  

The supported event types are:
- AdvancedHunting-IdentityDirectoryEvents
- AdvancedHunting-IdentityLogonEvents
- AdvancedHunting-IdentityQueryEvents
- AdvancedHunting-CloudAppEvents
